source.name: Colorado Plateau Rapid Ecoregion Assessment Management Question H2: Where are areas of concentrated recreation travel (OHV and other travel) located?
source.description: This map shows water-based recreation travel corridors (selected from NHD flowlines), and land-based recreation travel corridors (selected from BLM GTLF within federal / state lands and national trails).
